text: Romain Lopez, (born in 1989 in Moissac) is a French politician. He holds a master's degree in political science and another in history.. He joined the Front National at the end of 2013. Romain Lopez, as a member of the Rassemblement National was elected mayor of Moissac on June 28, 2020... ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Politicians from Occitanie Category:People from Tarn-et-Garonne
